# Documentation Standards — {{TEAM_NAME}}
_Maintained by Anchor and Cipher._

## Principles
- Lead with the answer (BLUF)
- One idea per section
- Consistent terminology — never use synonyms for technical terms

## Markdown Conventions
- H1 for document title only
- H2 for major sections
- H3 for subsections
- Code blocks for all code, commands, JSON
- Tables for structured comparisons

## File Naming
- Lowercase with hyphens: `my-document.md`
- Dates prefix for time-sensitive: `2026-02-26-decision.md`

## Required Metadata (top of every doc)
```
_Maintained by: <agent>. Last updated: <date>._
```

